g.text: Significant correlations (r) between marsh area and phenological changes, and the environmental variables, that is, year, sea‐
, temperature (T), precipitation (P), salinity (S), discharge (D), Oceanic Niño Index (ONI) from 1984 to 2014. All the
correlations between the variables are tested, but only significant correlations are shown in the table (P < 0.05)
